Author: tofu_snob
Text: It is possible that its due to bulimia. After 7 years of bulimia, my body goes through a variety of different physical symptoms. It might take a few days, weeks, or even months to start feeling better, but I highly encourage you to continue with your plan to keep meals down. Its also a good idea to try to get some extra sleep too. Good luck, and we are here for support!

Author: 3cats_in_atrenchcoat
Text: All of the above absolutely. and doubly so if your calorie intake is low.
